cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.NI 

This paper deals with the problem of controlling penetration testing tools, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a planning model that captures uncertainty and uses AI tools to generate attack plans, which falls under the subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the planning algorithms, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and network infrastructure (cs.NI).
